{"tid":749232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"他假扮美艷人妻約砲　小王爽後才知是男男性交","createTime":"2018-07-20T01:07:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T01:52:10.000Z","uid":122,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d4db012b7eeb9a29810b6ba73daf26c058748eab","tid":749232,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T01:07:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180720/640_cd3483e37f85a0655c929b08cb38927c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180720%2F640_cd3483e37f85a0655c929b08cb38927c.jpg&h=37c74804&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國南佛羅里達州一名32歲男子德紐摩斯特(Bryan Deneumostier)，常常男扮女裝，裝扮成美艷人妻，並在網路上找「小王」。多位「小王」與德紐摩斯特成功發生性關係，但之後這些「小王」才發現，跟他們做愛的不是女的，根本是個男的。<br />\n<br />\n據美國《Sun-sentinel》網站報導，警方調查發現，德紐摩斯特在過去4年，常常以網路名「susanleon33326」在網路平台上刊登廣告，自稱是一名美艷人妻，但寂寞難耐，想找小王洩慾。德紐摩斯特成功釣到多位「小王」，在跟這些男子見面時，德紐摩斯特也故意打扮成熟女，隨後德紐摩斯特就會就要求玩性遊戲，包括讓小王蒙眼，或者戴黑色護目鏡，意圖讓對方看不見「她」的真面目。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，德紐摩斯特也會事先架好偷拍攝影機，錄下兩人的性愛過程，並把畫面上傳到男男性愛網站「StraightBoyz」。警方表示，德紐摩斯特大約上傳600支影片，在案件爆發後目前已都下架。<br />\n<br />\n受害「小王」對警方表示，透過網站和德紐摩斯特約砲，看到德紐摩斯特時，都認為對方是美豔人妻，隨後兩人進行香豔刺激的性愛過程，大家都不知道「原來我被男的督了...」。受害人也表示，不知道德紐摩斯特偷拍。<br />\n<br />\n報導也指出，德紐摩斯特在今年6月和一名青少年約砲，這名青少年被報案失蹤，而警方在協尋的過程中，發現了該名青少年和德紐摩斯特在一處賓館開房間，德紐摩斯特的罪行才全部被揭發。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nesncom.files.wordpress.com/2014/06/858262469.gif?w=600&amp;h=338\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnesncom.files.wordpress.com%2F2014%2F06%2F858262469.gif%3Fw%3D600%26h%3D338&h=b26cc808&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d1502492ed05f8351f579ef27197b19328b67b2","tid":749232,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T01:13:03.000Z","msg":"600支一支都無得睇？"},{"pid":"ecb478355ead06e2bbe8ed148d563a0ea0d4f167","tid":749232,"uid":21917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T01:13:29.000Z","msg":"咁都扮到女人？"},{"pid":"633c0e89070fe1413593bfaec60b73be4171bfe3","tid":749232,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T01:16:47.000Z","msg":"今次連網絡瘋傳都無？"},{"pid":"dda476873bc4c6191c8b37ddb641257a81a54de3","tid":749232,"uid":64884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T01:18:47.000Z","msg":"支你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c7da27d8501454f61d18a81758c40abc414f9c8","tid":749232,"uid":68745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T01:20:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b802dd81a776717e3e8c5a0bc8be6ee833d0351a","tid":749232,"uid":46933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T01:23:41.000Z","msg":"「原來我被男的督了...」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔通佢地以為俾個女人篤緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98bcd160b1e7496d8b2071912fac6f4c817ba009","tid":749232,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T01:25:49.000Z","msg":"鬼佬多智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b88e93f794d6d59761294a6d353f002556664f6","tid":749232,"uid":139203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"633c0e89070fe1413593bfaec60b73be4171bfe3","tid":749232,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T01:16:47.000Z","msg":"今次連網絡瘋傳都無？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T01:26:58.000Z","msg":"想睇自己google susanleon33326 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0806d55ef5ffac9d039cfbd30296107a6ce3665","tid":749232,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T01:28:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> you</span></span>"},{"pid":"f978dba021a4354ddf16b2a5db3e6e8e78775323","tid"